Definition: surgical procedure that creates an opening from the ileum through the abdominal wall to function as an anus
Example: performed in cases of cancer of the colon or ulcerative colitis
Synonyms: ostomy, surgical, procedure, that, creates, an, opening, from, the, ileum, through, abdominal, wall, to, function, as, anus, performed, in, cases, of, cancer, colon, or, ulcerative, colitis
Category: noun.act
